    "desc": "Multiple attempts to access EC2 Instance Metadata Service (IMDS) from a container in the production namespace. The container 'nginx' in pod 'webapp-frontend' is attempting to retrieve IAM credentials via the metadata endpoint. This is a known SSRF attack vector used for credential theft in containerized environments.",
